1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:00:04,500 --> 00:00:05,110
Tong Xi,

3
00:00:06,430 --> 00:00:07,950
do you know

4
00:00:08,790 --> 00:00:09,710
how important you are to me?

5
00:00:11,540 --> 00:00:13,190
Why are you saying that all of a sudden?

6
00:00:15,830 --> 00:00:17,470
I'm going to leave Xi Hai by tomorrow.

7
00:00:18,270 --> 00:00:21,070
This time, I don't want to
leave any regrets behind.

8
00:00:21,710 --> 00:00:22,790
I want you to know

9
00:00:23,230 --> 00:00:24,740
what you mean to me.

10
00:00:25,670 --> 00:00:27,790
I don't want our story to end here.

11
00:00:29,590 --> 00:00:30,190
Do you understand me?

12
00:00:33,110 --> 00:00:34,870
I need to thank you no matter what.

13
00:00:35,350 --> 00:00:37,550
You provided me with the best memories
during my youth.

14
00:00:38,110 --> 00:00:39,380
That fact will never change.

15
00:00:40,950 --> 00:00:41,950
Thank you for caring about me.

16
00:00:42,630 --> 00:00:44,510
Thank you for your trust
and companionship.

17
00:00:45,430 --> 00:00:46,270
Because of you,

18
00:00:46,860 --> 00:00:48,670
there's no regret in my youth.

19
00:00:50,070 --> 00:00:51,390
We will see each other again soon.

20
00:00:52,750 --> 00:00:53,710
Remember to write to me.

21
00:01:18,470 --> 00:01:19,390
[Lin Nan Yi,]

22
00:01:19,789 --> 00:01:20,830
[do you know something?]

23
00:01:21,470 --> 00:01:23,350
[I'm starting to miss you]

24
00:01:23,990 --> 00:01:25,750
[even though
you haven't left the town yet.]

25
00:01:37,810 --> 00:01:42,130
[Summer Again]

26
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:48,640
[Summer Again, Chapter 24, Eternal Summer,
[Adapted from Huo He's comic, "Mint Love".]

27
00:02:14,430 --> 00:02:16,390
[Yi Ming, please do me a favour.]

28
00:02:23,270 --> 00:02:24,550
Do you feel disheartened?

29
00:02:25,550 --> 00:02:26,310
Nope.

30
00:02:26,829 --> 00:02:28,630
Stop pretending.
Look at your swollen eyes.

31
00:02:30,910 --> 00:02:32,990
By the way, is Lin Nan Yi leaving today?

32
00:02:32,990 --> 00:02:33,910
Aren't you going to see him off?

33
00:02:38,990 --> 00:02:39,510
But, you have a point.

34
00:02:40,230 --> 00:02:41,829
Farewell is a heartbreaking process.

35
00:02:42,070 --> 00:02:43,150
You'll see him again soon anyway.

36
00:02:44,070 --> 00:02:45,750
Besides, you still have me by your side.

37
00:02:46,790 --> 00:02:47,990
I will always stay by your side.

38
00:02:49,910 --> 00:02:50,350
By the way,

39
00:02:50,470 --> 00:02:52,150
how's your preparation for
the monthly exam?

40
00:02:55,230 --> 00:02:57,190
I feel like crying even more
when you mention that.

41
00:02:59,990 --> 00:03:00,470
Let's go.

42
00:03:34,630 --> 00:03:35,470
Be careful.

43
00:03:36,630 --> 00:03:37,420
-I'm sorry.
-I'm sorry.

44
00:03:38,870 --> 00:03:39,510
Thank you.

45
00:04:27,650 --> 00:04:29,720
[Hope we meet again]

46
00:04:42,830 --> 00:04:45,110
Tong Xi, I'll ask Wang Yi Ming
to send you there!

47
00:04:49,630 --> 00:04:50,390
Tong Xi!

48
00:04:53,550 --> 00:04:55,590
Get on the bike!

49
00:05:02,810 --> 00:05:10,160
[Waiting Room]

50
00:05:26,990 --> 00:05:27,710
We're here.

51
00:05:32,270 --> 00:05:34,110
Sorry about this.

52
00:05:59,700 --> 00:06:09,730
[Counter 1]

53
00:06:13,670 --> 00:06:14,390
Tong Xi.

54
00:06:27,070 --> 00:06:27,870
I was waiting for you.

55
00:06:44,909 --> 00:06:47,510
How did you know I would come today?

56
00:06:49,150 --> 00:06:49,790
Based on my instinct.

57
00:06:50,870 --> 00:06:52,740
I changed my ticket
to the next bus ticket.

58
00:06:53,790 --> 00:06:56,030
If you didn't come for the next two hours,

59
00:06:56,990 --> 00:06:58,350
maybe I would've left the town.

60
00:07:00,110 --> 00:07:01,270
It's lucky that I got here in time.

61
00:07:02,830 --> 00:07:03,510
Tong Xi,

62
00:07:04,830 --> 00:07:06,910
I was pretty happy

63
00:07:07,750 --> 00:07:08,630
when I saw you coming.

64
00:07:11,630 --> 00:07:12,670
You're leaving soon.

65
00:07:13,070 --> 00:07:14,070
Only at this time, I realised

66
00:07:14,430 --> 00:07:16,350
how important you are to me.

67
00:07:18,550 --> 00:07:19,670
Now that I think about it,

68
00:07:20,390 --> 00:07:22,710
it seems like I didn't bid you
a proper farewell.

69
00:07:28,630 --> 00:07:29,190
What is this?

70
00:07:29,910 --> 00:07:31,470
You can write a letter to me right now.

71
00:07:34,390 --> 00:07:36,070
In the past when
mobile phones don't exist,

72
00:07:36,150 --> 00:07:37,350
people who are in two different places

73
00:07:37,350 --> 00:07:38,670
will write letters to each other.

74
00:07:39,390 --> 00:07:40,630
Let's write letters to each other

75
00:07:40,820 --> 00:07:42,190
since we're free right now.

76
00:07:45,950 --> 00:07:47,030
When I was young,

77
00:07:47,030 --> 00:07:48,230
I wrote so many letters to you,

78
00:07:48,230 --> 00:07:48,950
yet you didn't receive them at all.

79
00:07:49,190 --> 00:07:50,550
Now, I'm sure you'll receive my letters.

80
00:07:51,230 --> 00:07:52,950
Let me think about what I should write.

81
00:07:53,070 --> 00:07:54,310
You can write whatever you want.

82
00:08:30,150 --> 00:08:33,070
You can read it after you get on the bus.

83
00:08:33,990 --> 00:08:35,830
I know. You too.

84
00:08:37,630 --> 00:08:39,470
Get on the bus. We're departing.

85
00:08:40,270 --> 00:08:42,190
I'll leave now.

86
00:08:45,190 --> 00:08:45,830
Goodbye.

87
00:08:46,950 --> 00:08:47,470
Goodbye.

88
00:08:52,270 --> 00:08:52,900
Nan Yi!

89
00:08:54,790 --> 00:08:55,350
What's the matter?

90
00:08:57,590 --> 00:08:58,470
Have a safe trip.

91
00:09:10,710 --> 00:09:13,710
[Actually, I have plenty to tell you.]

92
00:09:14,350 --> 00:09:16,430
[But I don't know where to start.]

93
00:09:17,550 --> 00:09:20,470
[I feel heartbroken when I know that
we're going to be separated.]

94
00:09:21,550 --> 00:09:24,590
[Lin Nan Yi, are we really
going to be apart from one another?]

95
00:09:30,910 --> 00:09:33,150
I wonder how Lin and Tong Xi are doing?

96
00:09:33,790 --> 00:09:36,030
I guess they're crying while
bidding farewell to each other.

97
00:09:37,630 --> 00:09:40,100
Did you become a retard?
I'm talking to you, you know?

98
00:09:46,820 --> 00:09:47,910
What's wrong with you?

99
00:09:48,190 --> 00:09:52,310
I miss Lin already!

100
00:09:53,710 --> 00:09:58,670
My Lin has left me!

101
00:09:59,580 --> 00:10:04,550
I feel heartbroken!

102
00:10:06,390 --> 00:10:07,310
Enough already.

103
00:10:07,310 --> 00:10:09,550
You're crying as if
something had happened to Lin.

104
00:10:09,590 --> 00:10:10,910
I'm sure he'll return here.

105
00:10:12,030 --> 00:10:12,870
Stop crying.

106
00:10:19,990 --> 00:10:21,190
Give me a hug!

107
00:11:17,070 --> 00:11:18,590
[Lin Nan Yi, how are you?]

108
00:11:18,950 --> 00:11:20,230
[This is my letter for you.]

109
00:11:20,990 --> 00:11:23,230
[But, I don't plan to send them to you.]

110
00:11:23,830 --> 00:11:25,300
[I'm going to keep my stories with me.]

111
00:11:25,430 --> 00:11:26,510
[I'll tell you about them]

112
00:11:26,710 --> 00:11:29,350
[when you come back.]

113
00:11:48,590 --> 00:11:50,230
[The beach we frequent]

114
00:11:50,270 --> 00:11:52,350
[is so windy that we can't
walk in a straight line.]

115
00:11:52,830 --> 00:11:53,910
[But, ever since you left,]

116
00:11:54,190 --> 00:11:55,780
[I have never been there.]

117
00:11:58,030 --> 00:11:58,990
[As long as I'm on a break,]

118
00:11:59,150 --> 00:12:01,150
[I'll practise ballet
in the practice room.]

119
00:12:01,470 --> 00:12:03,430
[Mr Xu has been praising me lately.]

120
00:12:03,750 --> 00:12:04,670
Yes, that's right.

121
00:12:06,950 --> 00:12:08,630
[Tao Zi has been busy as well.]

122
00:12:09,030 --> 00:12:09,830
[Do you know this?]

123
00:12:10,030 --> 00:12:12,230
[Xu Ao actually apologised to her.]

124
00:12:12,390 --> 00:12:14,030
[He even handed over
the drama club to her.]

125
00:12:15,190 --> 00:12:16,710
[As for how he apologised to her,]

126
00:12:16,790 --> 00:12:17,990
[Tao Zi didn't tell us about that.]

127
00:12:18,340 --> 00:12:19,470
[According to her,]

128
00:12:19,470 --> 00:12:21,190
[Xu Ao was kneeling on the ground]

129
00:12:21,420 --> 00:12:22,710
[and begging for her forgiveness.]

130
00:12:22,710 --> 00:12:25,230
I'm sorry! Please forgive me!

131
00:12:26,190 --> 00:12:28,590
[Tao Zi has no choice but to forgive him.]

132
00:12:32,830 --> 00:12:34,110
[But, I don't know why,]

133
00:12:34,350 --> 00:12:36,750
[it seems that Tao Zi looks disappointed.]

134
00:12:37,510 --> 00:12:38,550
[The dialogue]

135
00:12:38,550 --> 00:12:40,350
[between them]

136
00:12:38,990 --> 00:12:41,010
[Tao Zi, hope you become prettier and slimmer,
from Qinghe]

137
00:12:40,510 --> 00:12:41,510
[might not be that important.]

138
00:12:42,070 --> 00:12:43,100
[In our youth,]

139
00:12:43,150 --> 00:12:45,670
[there are always mistakes
that need no explanations.]

140
00:12:45,790 --> 00:12:47,310
There will be regrets as well.

141
00:13:04,430 --> 00:13:05,150
Nan Yi,

142
00:13:06,270 --> 00:13:07,070
say,

143
00:13:07,740 --> 00:13:09,310
will we ever meet the people

144
00:13:10,110 --> 00:13:11,430
who had left us?

145
00:13:14,460 --> 00:13:16,660
Even after so long, I still think

146
00:13:17,980 --> 00:13:19,390
that we will meet each other again.

147
00:13:22,380 --> 00:13:24,140
Just like the meaning of mint,

148
00:13:25,110 --> 00:13:26,590
even after numerous meetings,

149
00:13:28,540 --> 00:13:31,270
I still hope to see you again.

150
00:13:49,470 --> 00:13:51,270
[The summer after your departure]

151
00:13:51,310 --> 00:13:52,510
[came at a moment's notice.]

152
00:13:53,030 --> 00:13:54,110
[During this summer,]

153
00:13:54,230 --> 00:13:56,270
[a lot of people had left Xi Hai.]

154
00:13:56,670 --> 00:13:57,430
[Wei Ze,]

155
00:13:57,550 --> 00:13:58,350
[Xu Ao,]

156
00:13:58,550 --> 00:13:59,550
[and Sister Mi Ya..]

157
00:14:09,670 --> 00:14:13,280
[Farewell]

158
00:14:13,500 --> 00:14:20,230
[Blue Elephant]

159
00:14:13,790 --> 00:14:15,470
[Blue Elephant is closed now.]

160
00:14:15,790 --> 00:14:17,990
[Sister Mi Ya told us that
she bought the plane ticket]

161
00:14:17,990 --> 00:14:18,790
[two days ago.]

162
00:14:18,990 --> 00:14:21,140
[After that, she closed the shop.]

163
00:14:21,750 --> 00:14:23,310
[Seeing her picture]

164
00:14:23,310 --> 00:14:24,990
[together with Andre under
the Eiffel Tower,]

165
00:14:25,430 --> 00:14:27,030
[I guess she's happy.]

166
00:14:33,710 --> 00:14:35,390
[Of course, I have good news
for you as well.]

167
00:14:35,790 --> 00:14:37,100
[After Sister Mi Ya's departure,]

168
00:14:37,190 --> 00:14:38,420
[I adopted Monroe.]

169
00:14:38,950 --> 00:14:40,670
[In the end, I realised that it's a...]

170
00:14:43,390 --> 00:14:44,950
Are you out of your mind?

171
00:14:46,510 --> 00:14:49,790
[And, my mother has been
putting on makeup lately.]

172
00:14:50,110 --> 00:14:51,830
[She dolls herself up every day.]

173
00:14:52,190 --> 00:14:53,790
[That day, she went out
to have a meal with someone.]

174
00:14:54,260 --> 00:14:55,580
[I was prepared]

175
00:14:55,580 --> 00:14:56,630
[to fight against that scumbag.]

176
00:14:57,070 --> 00:14:58,150
[In the end,]

177
00:14:58,190 --> 00:14:59,950
[I realised that her partner
was actually my father.]

178
00:15:01,510 --> 00:15:02,620
Hello, Tong Tong?

179
00:15:04,070 --> 00:15:06,700
[No wonder my father's career
is proceeding smoothly.]

180
00:15:07,110 --> 00:15:08,870
[It's due to the power of love.]

181
00:15:25,710 --> 00:15:26,670
Lin Nan Yi,

182
00:15:27,750 --> 00:15:29,190
it's winter now.

183
00:15:29,750 --> 00:15:32,350
My father's new book, Ah Nuan's Travel,

184
00:15:32,510 --> 00:15:33,750
has finally been published.

185
00:15:42,230 --> 00:15:43,750
When will you come back?

186
00:16:04,990 --> 00:16:06,400
[Mint Love]

187
00:16:06,590 --> 00:16:08,070
Guru Qinghe, please bless me

188
00:16:08,980 --> 00:16:10,030
so that I can pass the audition.

189
00:16:10,990 --> 00:16:12,940
Last candidate, Candidate 3078.

190
00:16:12,940 --> 00:16:13,590
Coming.

191
00:16:27,270 --> 00:16:28,110
Nice to meet you.

192
00:16:28,150 --> 00:16:29,660
I'm Candidate 3078.

193
00:16:29,750 --> 00:16:31,630
I come from Xi Hai High School,
Lindong Province.

194
00:16:32,070 --> 00:16:34,510
Tong Xi, you specialise in ballet.

195
00:16:34,910 --> 00:16:37,510
Do you want to get into an art troupe
in the future?

196
00:16:37,750 --> 00:16:39,150
Or are you taking the exam for now?

197
00:16:39,310 --> 00:16:40,830
Are you considering
a different career path in the future?

198
00:16:41,310 --> 00:16:41,830
I...

199
00:16:44,990 --> 00:16:46,310
I don't have a designated direction.

200
00:16:46,750 --> 00:16:48,070
I just like ballet.

201
00:16:48,390 --> 00:16:50,460
No matter what kind of career
I'll have in the future,

202
00:16:50,790 --> 00:16:52,510
it's fine as long as I can continue
to do ballet.

203
00:16:53,030 --> 00:16:54,390
Alright, you may begin.

204
00:17:07,349 --> 00:17:09,390
[Lin Nan Yi, do you know this?]

205
00:17:09,819 --> 00:17:12,270
[Today, I've achieved a great feat.]

206
00:17:12,869 --> 00:17:15,869
[When I was dancing,
I was reminded of the times]

207
00:17:16,190 --> 00:17:18,829
[when I was nervous in front of Senior
Wei Ze during the art club's interview.]

208
00:17:19,710 --> 00:17:21,550
[Back then,]

209
00:17:21,589 --> 00:17:23,230
[I didn't understand why
I was that worried.]

210
00:17:23,790 --> 00:17:25,030
[Now, I finally understand why.]

211
00:17:25,310 --> 00:17:26,990
[Only when people]

212
00:17:26,990 --> 00:17:29,030
[know clearly what they want]

213
00:17:29,350 --> 00:17:31,790
[will they be truly fearless.]

214
00:17:32,710 --> 00:17:33,990
[When an ordinary girl]

215
00:17:33,990 --> 00:17:35,790
[finds her true self,]

216
00:17:36,020 --> 00:17:38,070
[she'll be able to transform
into the White Swan.]

217
00:17:38,750 --> 00:17:40,630
[Lin Nan Yi, thank you.]

218
00:17:40,830 --> 00:17:42,670
[Thank you for helping me
to find my true self.]

219
00:18:13,540 --> 00:18:15,430
This Lin Nan Yi is really something.

220
00:18:16,030 --> 00:18:17,990
I help you water your mint plants
the moment I came back.

221
00:18:18,380 --> 00:18:19,590
Yet, you didn't reply
to my message at all.

222
00:18:20,310 --> 00:18:21,230
What a scumbag.

223
00:18:42,910 --> 00:18:45,630
Tao Zhu, ask Wang Yi Ming
to come to the mint garden.

224
00:18:46,310 --> 00:18:48,670
I think a thief snuck into
Lin Nan Yi's house.

225
00:19:45,590 --> 00:19:46,150
What are you doing?

226
00:19:47,180 --> 00:19:47,870
Don't you recognise me?

227
00:19:49,750 --> 00:19:50,590
Lin Nan Yi?

228
00:19:51,750 --> 00:19:52,390
You're alive?

229
00:19:53,190 --> 00:19:54,070
It's really you?

230
00:19:54,270 --> 00:19:55,230
Why are you back?

231
00:19:56,710 --> 00:19:57,390
Wait,

232
00:19:57,950 --> 00:19:59,390
don't tell me you argued with your mother?

233
00:20:00,030 --> 00:20:01,710
Don't tell me you came back
because you left home?

234
00:20:02,150 --> 00:20:02,750
No.

235
00:20:03,580 --> 00:20:04,670
I just finished my exams.

236
00:20:05,270 --> 00:20:06,110
I reached home earlier than you

237
00:20:06,710 --> 00:20:07,710
because I wanted to surprise you.

238
00:20:09,390 --> 00:20:11,230
Exams? Surprise?

239
00:20:12,110 --> 00:20:13,030
What do you mean?

240
00:20:13,390 --> 00:20:14,710
I thought you transferred to
another school?

241
00:20:16,430 --> 00:20:18,980
I did, but my status is still the same.

242
00:20:20,190 --> 00:20:21,270
I still need to come back

243
00:20:21,710 --> 00:20:22,830
for the NCEE after my audition.

244
00:20:24,030 --> 00:20:24,700
NCEE?

245
00:20:25,830 --> 00:20:26,990
Does that mean you're staying?

246
00:20:27,340 --> 00:20:28,390
We don't need to be separated

247
00:20:28,710 --> 00:20:29,910
for the first half of the year
before NCEE.

248
00:20:31,710 --> 00:20:32,830
If we're lucky enough,

249
00:20:33,230 --> 00:20:34,470
we'll get into the same university.

250
00:20:34,990 --> 00:20:35,790
By then,

251
00:20:36,390 --> 00:20:37,790
we will never have to
part from each other.

252
00:20:41,070 --> 00:20:43,590
Tong Xi, I'll take the
NCEE together with you.

253
00:20:52,310 --> 00:20:53,150
Why are you crying?

254
00:20:54,070 --> 00:20:54,950
Lin Nan Yi,

255
00:20:55,350 --> 00:20:56,500
do you know how bored I am

256
00:20:56,500 --> 00:20:57,630
when you weren't around?

257
00:20:58,870 --> 00:20:59,790
It's okay now.

258
00:21:00,550 --> 00:21:01,630
I'm back now, aren't I?

259
00:21:02,590 --> 00:21:03,220
Stop crying.

260
00:21:08,590 --> 00:21:10,870
[20th January 2016.]

261
00:21:11,430 --> 00:21:13,030
[The night sky is filled with stars.]

262
00:21:13,510 --> 00:21:14,310
[Lin Nan Yi,]

263
00:21:14,590 --> 00:21:16,630
[I think I'll stop writing for now.]

264
00:21:17,150 --> 00:21:19,550
[Because, the person I was waiting for]

265
00:21:19,670 --> 00:21:20,910
[has finally returned home.]

266
00:22:00,990 --> 00:22:02,420
Do you guys think
those are lottery tickets?

267
00:22:02,420 --> 00:22:03,510
You can claim your prize now.

268
00:22:08,140 --> 00:22:09,190
Da Cheng?

269
00:22:10,890 --> 00:22:13,490
