You could've seen the result
for yourself on the Internet,

272
00:22:19,990 --> 00:22:21,550
yet you have to come here personally.

273
00:22:22,150 --> 00:22:23,390
I'm sure you guys wanted to
surprise each other.

274
00:22:30,630 --> 00:22:31,470
You two

275
00:22:31,990 --> 00:22:32,790
should live your life

276
00:22:33,150 --> 00:22:35,150
and study hard when you two
get into university.

