297
00:23:22,230 --> 00:23:23,390
What are you doing?

298
00:23:23,630 --> 00:23:24,430
I'm stopping.

299
00:23:25,500 --> 00:23:25,940
I'm exhausted.

300
00:23:27,830 --> 00:23:28,350
I need to take a break.

301
00:23:38,870 --> 00:23:42,110
Say, why are we stuck together?

302
00:23:42,550 --> 00:23:44,190
You were my neighbour since young.

303
00:23:44,350 --> 00:23:46,590
