we're attending university.

304
00:23:47,060 --> 00:23:47,990
This is so annoying.

305
00:23:48,350 --> 00:23:49,550
Enough already.

306
00:23:50,270 --> 00:23:51,790
I've lost count of the times
you asked me that question.

307
00:23:52,390 --> 00:23:53,310
Are you done?

308
00:23:53,710 --> 00:23:54,790
If you're done with your break,

309
00:23:54,790 --> 00:23:55,670
we should go.

310
00:23:55,790 --> 00:23:56,860
They're still waiting for us.

311
00:23:57,350 --> 00:23:58,510
Why are you in such a hurry?

312
00:24:00,550 --> 00:24:02,430
We haven't had a proper chat

313
00:24:02,430 --> 00:24:03,590
after we took our certification.

314
00:24:04,550 --> 00:24:05,660
Why are you in a hurry to see them?

315
00:24:06,230 --> 00:24:07,150
There's nothing we can't talk about

316
00:24:07,150 --> 00:24:08,790
